{"tid":1871533,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"在全世界發起#ShoutForFreedom挑戰,","createTime":"2020-02-09T13:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T03:14:47.000Z","uid":252840,"like":27,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"49d696fa9cc6fb4a8e45c8e34453dab120728ebf","tid":1871533,"uid":252840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T13:39:31.000Z","msg":"唔知大家記唔記得2014 年ice bucket challenge挑戰，當時既呢個campaign為漸涷人協會籌得近八千萬美金<br />\n<br />\n李文亮既死係反攻中共既最佳時機，當上面個個都話要言論自由之時，我地要係國際社會上都做岀一個支持中國有<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>言論自由既氣勢<br />\n<br />\n所以我希望由香港發起#ShoutForFreedom 既挑戰<br />\n<br />\n玩法好簡單：<br />\n拍片，走係街上面，突然對住條街既人咆哮 &quot;我要言論自由, I Shout for freedom, 我要言論自由(普通話)&quot; 用三種語言叫<br />\n<br />\n愈大聲愈好，嚇到條街d人愈大反應愈好<br />\n再tag 3個朋友，要佢地參加挑戰<br />\n<br />\n再加hash tag <span style=\"color: red;\">#ShoutForFreedom</span>,#<span style=\"color: red;\">我要言論自由</span><span style=\"color: red;\">#不要第二個李文亮#FreeHongKong#FreeChina</span><br />\n<br />\n要造成個氣勢要全世界人一齊嗌，嚇到班中共狗賴尿為止"},{"pid":"f8a2768e12b27aaf3139acefeeee2f159c0093fb","tid":1871533,"uid":252840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T13:40:10.000Z","msg":"推9佢"},{"pid":"3fd5b647958f1539f3ecf46fe80f351898281f4f","tid":1871533,"uid":252840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T13:40:23.000Z","msg":"推9佢"},{"pid":"1b4ae2b975a4aac0280e3418d23fc15a7f6e1bee","tid":1871533,"uid":252840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T13:40:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8a657582eb075027e1ca6d3ca70c34b31865948","tid":1871533,"uid":252840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T13:40:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cab1e411fbfbe24c9a1b46a6dc63fb27c81cf823","tid":1871533,"uid":252840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T13:41:01.000Z","msg":"ppppush"},{"pid":"eddf0cb8d286ab249558acf2eaf8b114b8f26e5a","tid":1871533,"uid":252840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2